SELECT
    customer.id
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://scbpocdev.dfs.core.windows.net/sqlservlessinternalselfmanaged/account.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) AS account
    JOIN
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://scbpocdev.dfs.core.windows.net/sqlservlessinternalselfmanaged/customer.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) AS customer
    on account.customer_id = customer.id
